title: EastEnders.EXTRA.Backstage.Live.P1
description:
EastEnders.EXTRA.Backstage.Live.P1

Part 1:

Zoe Ball goes live on set immediately upon completion of todays EastEnders live episode. She has complete behind the scenes access to the cast and set. 
Cast & crew current & past join her to offer insight on the iconic soaps legendary history right up to the present day mega mystery. 

First broadcast: 20 Feb 2015
